      "outputs": [],
      "title": "Incremental changes described here",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "## Workflow 6: End-to-End Isolation\n\n### What Changed\n\n**All isolated nodes are now connected to each other**, forming a complete self-contained pipeline in the child process:\n\nUNETLoader_ZIMG → ModelSampling_ZIMG → KSampler_ZIMG → VAEDecode_ZIMG → SaveImage_ZIMG\n\nCLIPLoader_ZIMG → CLIPTextEncode_ZIMG → KSampler_ZIMG\n\nVAELoader_ZIMG → VAEDecode_ZIMG\n\nThe host-side pipeline still exists above but the isolated pipeline runs independently.\n\n### What Crosses the Process Boundary\n\nEverything runs in the child. Cross-boundary traffic is limited to:\n\n- **Model weights** loaded via `folder_paths` proxy (file paths resolved on host)\n- **Progress updates** sent back to host UI\n- **Saved images** written via host filesystem\n\n### Architecture\n\n```\nHost Process\n  │ folder_paths (FolderPathsProxy)\n  │ model_management (ModelMgmtProxy)\n  │ progress (ProgressProxy)\n  │ prompt_server (PromptServerStub)\n  │\nChild Process\n  └─ Full pipeline: load → encode →\n     sample → decode → save\n```\n\nService proxies provide the ComfyUI infrastructure the child needs without exposing the host process.\n"
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#000"
    },
    {
      "id": 84,
      "type": "MarkdownNote",
      "pos": [
        561.9523716308595,
        1026.0364172790512
      ],
      "size": [
        510,
        680
      ],
      "flags": {},
      "order": 14,
      "mode": 0,
      "inputs": [],
      "outputs": [],
      "title": "Code from custom node",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "## Code: Service Proxies\n\n### Module Patching (`comfy/isolation/adapter.py`)\n\nIn the child process, ComfyUI modules are replaced with RPC proxies:\n\n```python\n# handle_api_registration() patches\n# child-side modules:\nfor name in dir(proxy_instance):\n    if not name.startswith('_'):\n        setattr(\n            folder_paths, name,\n            getattr(proxy_instance, name)\n        )\n```\n\nThe child's `folder_paths.get_folder_paths()` transparently calls the host via RPC.\n\n### Service Proxy Files\n\n`comfy/isolation/proxies/` directory:\n\n| File | Service |\n|:--|:--|\n| `folder_paths_proxy.py` | Path resolution |\n| `model_management_proxy.py` | VRAM management |\n| `prompt_server_impl.py` | Route registration |\n| `progress_proxy.py` | Progress bars |\n| `utils_proxy.py` | Utility functions |\n| `web_directory_proxy.py` | Web asset serving |\n| `helper_proxies.py` | Special INPUT_TYPES |\n\n### Extension Wrapper\n\n`comfy/isolation/extension_wrapper.py` — `ComfyNodeExtension` handles child-side node discovery, V1+V3 node registration, and `execute_node()` dispatch.\n\n### Runtime Helpers\n\n`comfy/isolation/runtime_helpers.py` — `build_stub_class()` creates host-side stub nodes that dispatch execution to the child via RPC.\n"
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#000"
    },
